<p>从井冈山上官兵待遇一扁担平到延安时期的开小灶；从与放权改革时代同步的后勤社会化，到当下内卷化的专业供应体系；我们试图揭开机关食堂鲜为人知的前世今生与世相百态。</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: 黑体;"><span style="color: #3366ff;"><a href="http://www.nbweekly.com/news/special/201105/26123.aspx" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.nbweekly.com/photocenter/2011/201118/a/P634414893165391176.jpg" alt="机关食堂的秘密_1" /></a></span></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: 黑体;"><span style="color: #3366ff;"><a href="http://www.nbweekly.com/news/special/201105/26123.aspx" target="_blank">吃在部委</a></span></span></span></p>
