<p><img src="http://www.nbweekly.com/photocenter/2011/201119/a/P634420207409021529.jpg" alt="地理_6" /></p>
<p>棕榈糖</p>
<p><img src="http://www.nbweekly.com/photocenter/2011/201119/a/P634420207415729541.jpg" alt="地理_7" /></p>
